{"tid":1847224,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府：公務員農曆新年假期後暫改為在家工作","createTime":"2020-01-28T03:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T06:23:52.000Z","uid":20933,"like":48,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"51e90f374c1ad70a027e1cf456ee6aa08c4229cf","tid":1847224,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:37:05.000Z","msg":"政府安排僱員特別上班安排，以減低疫情在社區擴散的風險，除提供緊急和必須公共服務的人員外，政府僱員在農曆新年假期後無需返回寫字樓辦公，改為留在家中工作。有關安排暫定實行至二月二日，政府屆時會再檢視情況。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人呼籲私人機構在可行情況下，作類似安排。"},{"pid":"bfe47ed89cfecca6f1047233e92ada29d4ffd110","tid":1847224,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:37:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1256527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1256527&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=1ae909d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1256527</a>"},{"pid":"97c1f069a8b2ed55e02727886581e3c6a13e9798","tid":1847224,"uid":81084,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:38:15.000Z","msg":"政府帶頭home office"},{"pid":"0a804e896f74f6d2b9b353acd8d833f9c1d2b853","tid":1847224,"uid":131188,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:38:25.000Z","msg":"政府有啲咩位可以在家工作, 林奠?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c44b05b77f14042a1ffb59bfe34f5e16cf9bee5","tid":1847224,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"［行動］呼籲策反海關入境，陀槍攻狗屋<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846551</a>"},{"pid":"f2a75ec62292b0fe1841f2c0f0696bb76066866b","tid":1847224,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-